1938;;Sexton Blake and the Hooded Terror;;British;;George King;;George Curzon, Tod Slaughter;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sexton_Blake_and_the_Hooded_Terror;;The film - described as the best in the Blake series of 1930s movies[3][4] - features the character of Sexton Blake and his efforts to defeat a major crime organisation headed by Michael Larron, a 'sort of Moriarty figure'.[5]